show.description: In a world where legacy and ambition collide, the heiress of the powerful Kings Corp joins Stream Corp as an undercover intern to prove her worth. But her journey takes a sharp turn when two mysterious interns show up sharing the same identity. As secrets unravel and loyalties blur, corporate games become a dangerous masquerade.
